rComments: Amazing professor who is always willing to help and is friendly! The lectures were clear and the exams were fair.

Great teacher and explains stuff well. You can tell she's really interested in the material she teaches though because she tends to get excited and go pretty fast at times, which can be hard to follow. Exams were pretty hard/tricky. Also, she's super hot.

Always ready to help if you need it, but has confusing lectures sometimes. The lectures tend to be long and she speaks fast, but overall the concepts aren't too hard. You really do need to study for the course though and know exact definitions, etc.
Lots of big ideas to remember
